Title: Fionna and Cake
Writer: Pendleton Ward (created by), Mark Banker (story by), Patrick McHale (story by), Kent Osborne (story by), Pendleton Ward (story by), Adam Muto, Rebecca Sugar
Actors: Jeremy Shada, Madeleine Martin, Roz Ryan, Tom Kenny
Plot: In a world where all the characters are different genders, the adventurer Fionna gets advice from her cat-friend Cake on her date with Prince Gumball.
